TitleEnglish: Kamen Rider W Forever: From A to Z, 26 Rapid-Succession Roars of Laughter
SummaryEnglish: 26 comedy-themed shorts (one for every letter of the alphabet) that were released by Toei to promote the Kamen Rider W summer movie, Kamen Rider W Forever: A to Z/The Gaia Memories of Fate. Following the trend started with Kamen Rider Kiva.
